high_descs: Go to the coffee maker in front of you.
Grab the cup from under the maker.
Go to the fridge on your right.
Place the cup in the fridge, then grab it out of the fridge.
Go back to the coffee maker to your left.
Place the cup back in the maker.
anns.task_desc: Chill a coffee cup for use in a coffee maker.

high_descs: Face the counter with the coffee maker in front of you.
Take the cup from the coffee maker in front of you.
Turn right and face the fridge to your left.
Place the cup inside the fridge then take it out.
Turn left then face the coffee maker to your right.
Place the cup in the coffee maker in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold cup in the coffee maker.

high_descs: Go to the coffee maker, straight ahead of you.
Grab the coffee cup from the coffee maker.
Turn to the refrigerator to your right.
Place the coffee cup in the refrigerator, on the top shelf, wait a moment for the coffee cup to chill, then remove the coffee cup from the refrigerator.
Go back to the coffee maker, on the dishwasher, to your left.
Place the coffee cup back on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled coffee cup in the coffee maker.
